{"metadata": {"page_hash": "f1787331401d0b91d42c530120854109816eef3c1dcc6bca06d9a7717ac8a5c8", "original_filename": "0000006201-21-000014_20210217x10k.pdf", "page_no": 119, "num_pages": 230, "original_width": 595, "original_height": 842, "coco_width": 1025, "coco_height": 1025, "collection": "sec_filings", "doc_category": "financial_reports"}, "form": [{"id_box": 74136, "box": [24.738352605042017, 12.525280878859803, 128.75003466386553, 10.613680225653297], "id_box_line": 0, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 12.525280878859803, 128.75003466386553, 10.613680225653297], "text": "Table of Contents", "category": "Page-header", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 255, 255], "name": "/QLUCAA+DejaVuSans-Bold", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74137, "box": [191.91092226890757, 37.08131057007131, 635.4743319327731, 10.613680225653297], "id_box_line": 1, "box_line": [191.91092226890757, 37.08131057007131, 635.4743319327731, 10.613680225653297], "text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS OF AMERICAN AIRLINES GROUP INC", "category": "Section-header", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QLUCAA+DejaVuSans-Bold", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74138, "box": [24.738352605042017, 79.87840825415685, 973.908621764706, 33.05838034441808], "id_box_line": 3, "box_line": [42.608149201680675, 79.87840825415685, 956.0388251680673, 10.604160629453645], "text": "In addition, following certain corporate events that occur prior to the maturity date or upon AAG\u2019s issuance of a notice of redemption, AAG will", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74138, "box": [24.738352605042017, 79.87840825415685, 973.908621764706, 33.05838034441808], "id_box_line": 4, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 91.10075831353925, 973.893479327731, 10.604172802850371], "text": "increase the conversion rate for a holder who elects to convert its Convertible Notes in connection with such corporate event or during the related", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74138, "box": [24.738352605042017, 79.87840825415685, 973.908621764706, 33.05838034441808], "id_box_line": 5, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 102.32310837292175, 958.4939999159664, 10.613680225653184], "text": "redemption period in certain circumstances by a specified number of shares of AAG common stock as described in the Convertible Notes Indenture.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74139, "box": [24.738352605042017, 121.96221793349173, 973.9145133613447, 77.96680760095012], "id_box_line": 6, "box_line": [42.608149201680675, 121.96221793349173, 956.0236827310923, 10.613680225653184], "text": "AAG will not have the right to redeem the Convertible Notes prior to July 5, 2023. On or after July 5, 2023 and on or before the 20th scheduled", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74139, "box": [24.738352605042017, 121.96221793349173, 973.9145133613447, 77.96680760095012], "id_box_line": 7, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 133.19407541567693, 973.9009557983194, 10.604172802850371], "text": "trading day immediately before the maturity date, AAG may redeem the Convertible Notes, in whole or in part, if the last reported sale price of AAG", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74139, "box": [24.738352605042017, 121.96221793349173, 973.9145133613447, 77.96680760095012], "id_box_line": 8, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 144.41642547505933, 973.9114642016807, 10.613680225653184], "text": "common stock has been at least 130% of the conversion price then in effect on (1) each of at least 20 trading days (whether or not consecutive)", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74139, "box": [24.738352605042017, 121.96221793349173, 973.9145133613447, 77.96680760095012], "id_box_line": 9, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 155.63877553444183, 973.8960116806724, 10.613680225653184], "text": "during the 30 consecutive trading days ending on, and including, the trading day immediately before the date AAG sends the related redemption", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74139, "box": [24.738352605042017, 121.96221793349173, 973.9145133613447, 77.96680760095012], "id_box_line": 10, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 166.86112559382423, 973.9145133613447, 10.613680225653184], "text": "notice; and (2) the trading day immediately before the date AAG sends such notice. In the case of any optional redemption, AAG will redeem the", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74139, "box": [24.738352605042017, 121.96221793349173, 973.9145133613447, 77.96680760095012], "id_box_line": 11, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 178.09299524940616, 973.9089490756304, 10.604160629453645], "text": "Convertible Notes at a redemption price equal to 100% of the principal amount of such Convertible Notes to be redeemed, plus accrued and unpaid", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74139, "box": [24.738352605042017, 121.96221793349173, 973.9145133613447, 77.96680760095012], "id_box_line": 12, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 189.31533313539194, 308.573197394958, 10.61369239904991], "text": "interest to, but excluding, the redemption date.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74140, "box": [24.738352605042017, 208.95445486935876, 973.9089490756304, 44.29023782660329], "id_box_line": 13, "box_line": [42.608149201680675, 208.95445486935876, 956.0364134033615, 10.613680225653184], "text": "If AAG undergoes a fundamental change described in the Convertible Notes Indenture prior to the maturity date of the Convertible Notes, except", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74140, "box": [24.738352605042017, 208.95445486935876, 973.9089490756304, 44.29023782660329], "id_box_line": 14, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 220.18631235154396, 973.9032642016808, 10.604172802850485], "text": "as described in the Convertible Notes Indenture, holders of the Convertible Notes may require AAG to repurchase for cash all or part of their", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74140, "box": [24.738352605042017, 208.95445486935876, 973.9089490756304, 44.29023782660329], "id_box_line": 15, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 231.40866241092635, 973.9089490756304, 10.604172802850485], "text": "Convertible Notes at a repurchase price equal to 100% of the principal amount of the Convertible Notes to be repurchased, plus accrued and unpaid", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74140, "box": [24.738352605042017, 208.95445486935876, 973.9089490756304, 44.29023782660329], "id_box_line": 16, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 242.63101247030886, 444.27194823529413, 10.613680225653184], "text": "interest to, but excluding, the fundamental change repurchase date.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74141, "box": [24.738352605042017, 262.27012203087884, 973.9145133613447, 55.51260005938241], "id_box_line": 17, "box_line": [42.608149201680675, 262.27012203087884, 956.044716764706, 10.613680225653184], "text": "The Convertible Notes Indenture provides for customary terms and covenants, including that upon certain events of default, either the Convertible", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74141, "box": [24.738352605042017, 262.27012203087884, 973.9145133613447, 55.51260005938241], "id_box_line": 18, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 273.50199168646077, 973.893479327731, 10.604160629453645], "text": "Notes Trustee or the holders of not less than 25% in aggregate principal amount of the Convertible Notes then outstanding may declare the unpaid", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74141, "box": [24.738352605042017, 262.27012203087884, 973.9145133613447, 55.51260005938241], "id_box_line": 19, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 284.72432957244655, 973.8960116806724, 10.61369239904991], "text": "principal amount of the Convertible Notes and accrued and unpaid interest, if any, thereon immediately due and payable. In the case of certain", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74141, "box": [24.738352605042017, 262.27012203087884, 973.9145133613447, 55.51260005938241], "id_box_line": 20, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 295.94669180522567, 973.9129457142857, 10.613668052256571], "text": "events of bankruptcy, insolvency or reorganization, the principal amount of the Convertible Notes together with accrued and unpaid interest thereon,", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74141, "box": [24.738352605042017, 262.27012203087884, 973.9145133613447, 55.51260005938241], "id_box_line": 21, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 307.16902969121145, 462.51407134453785, 10.613692399049796], "text": "if any, will automatically become and be immediately due and payable.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74142, "box": [24.738352605042017, 326.8176588479811, 973.9089490756304, 33.05838034441797], "id_box_line": 22, "box_line": [42.608149201680675, 326.8176588479811, 956.0209608823529, 10.604172802850371], "text": "As the Convertible Notes can be settled in cash upon conversion, for accounting purposes, the Convertible Notes were bifurcated into a debt", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74142, "box": [24.738352605042017, 326.8176588479811, 973.9089490756304, 33.05838034441797], "id_box_line": 23, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 338.0400089073635, 973.9089490756304, 10.613680225653184], "text": "component that was recorded at fair value and an equity component. The following table details the debt and equity components recognized related", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74142, "box": [24.738352605042017, 326.8176588479811, 973.9089490756304, 33.05838034441797], "id_box_line": 24, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 349.26235896674586, 409.64625957983196, 10.613680225653184], "text": "to the Convertible Notes as of December 31, 2020 (in millions):", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74143, "box": [24.738352605042017, 445.3751359857482, 973.9145133613447, 77.95728800475064], "id_box_line": 35, "box_line": [42.608149201680675, 445.3751359857482, 956.0365167647059, 10.613668052256571], "text": "The effective interest rate on the liability component approximates 20%. We recognized $61 million of interest expense in 2020 including $28", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74143, "box": [24.738352605042017, 445.3751359857482, 973.9145133613447, 77.95728800475064], "id_box_line": 36, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 456.597473871734, 973.9145133613447, 10.61369239904991], "text": "million of non-cash amortization of the debt discount and $33 million of contractual coupon interest. The remaining period over which the", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74143, "box": [24.738352605042017, 445.3751359857482, 973.9145133613447, 77.95728800475064], "id_box_line": 37, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 467.8293435273159, 973.9063133613446, 10.604160629453759], "text": "unamortized debt discount will be recognized as non-cash interest expense is five years as follows: $63 million in 2021, $77 million in 2022, $95", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74143, "box": [24.738352605042017, 445.3751359857482, 973.9145133613447, 77.95728800475064], "id_box_line": 38, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 479.0516935866983, 973.9129457142857, 10.604172802850371], "text": "million in 2023, $116 million in 2024 and $66 million in 2025. As previously discussed in Note 1(c), as of January 1, 2021, we early adopted the New", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74143, "box": [24.738352605042017, 445.3751359857482, 973.9145133613447, 77.95728800475064], "id_box_line": 39, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 490.2740436460808, 973.8960116806724, 10.613680225653184], "text": "Convertible Debt Standard. Accordingly, our unamortized debt discount as of January 1, 2021 was reduced by $389 million and the adjusted non-cash", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74143, "box": [24.738352605042017, 445.3751359857482, 973.9145133613447, 77.95728800475064], "id_box_line": 40, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 501.4963937054632, 973.9063133613446, 10.613680225653184], "text": "interest expense to be recognized over the next five years is as follows: $5 million in 2021, $6 million in 2022, $6 million in 2023, $7 million in 2024", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74143, "box": [24.738352605042017, 445.3751359857482, 973.9145133613447, 77.95728800475064], "id_box_line": 41, "box_line": [24.738352605042017, 512.7282511876484, 148.70675537815126, 10.604172802850428], "text": "and $4 million in 2025.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74144, "box": [42.608149201680675, 532.3673607482185, 701.5225566806723, 10.613680225653184], "id_box_line": 42, "box_line": [42.608149201680675, 532.3673607482185, 701.5225566806723, 10.613680225653184], "text": "At December 31, 2020, the if-converted value of the Convertible Notes did not exceed the principal amount.", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QFUCAA+DejaVuSans", "size": 13}}, {"id_box": 74145, "box": [42.608149201680675, 571.6550994655582, 135.6905835714286, 10.604172802850314], "id_box_line": 45, "box_line": [42.608149201680675, 571.6550994655582, 135.6905835714286, 10.604172802850314], "text": "5.000% Senior Notes", "category": "Text", "words": [], "linking": [], "font": {"color": [0, 0, 0, 255], "name": "/QTTCAA+DejaVuSans-Oblique", "size":